release of any medical information. Notwithstanding the provisions of R.S.
49:966(B)(12), the House and Senate committees on transportation, highways and
public works shall have oversight of the adoption of rules and regulations required
by this Subsection.
R. S. An applicant for any class of license may choose to donate one dollar
in addition to any license fee required by this Section to the Louisiana Military
Family Assistance Fund.
Section 2. This Act shall be known as "Riley's Law".
